Former U.K. Minister Hoon Takes Job Selling Helicopters, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-17T01:37:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-17/former-u-k-minister-hoon-takes-job-selling-helicopters-ft-says.html
Former U.K. Defence Secretary Geoff Hoon has taken a job as executive senior vice-president of
international business with helicopter manufacturer
AgustaWestland International Ltd., the Financial Times reported,
citing comments by Hoon.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 